   "source": [
    "**Note the class imbalance** — `joy` dominates (many fine-grained labels map to it: joy, amusement, approval, excitement, gratitude, love, optimism, relief, pride, admiration, desire, caring), while `fear` and `disgust` are rare. This is why we track **macro F1** (which weights every class equally) alongside accuracy, and why we use **class weights** during training."
