    "## 6. Pretrained Word Embeddings (GloVe)\n",
    "\n",
    "We initialize the embedding layer with **100-dimensional GloVe vectors** (`glove-wiki-gigaword-100`, trained on Wikipedia + Gigaword), loaded via `gensim`'s downloader API — no manual zip download needed.\n",
    "\n",
    "If GloVe cannot be downloaded in your environment (e.g. no internet access), the code below **automatically falls back to random initialization** with a warning, so the rest of the notebook still runs end-to-end."
   ]
  },
